    "You just need to invoke the make_graph function with the required parameter to print the graphs.The structure to call the `make_graph` function is `make_graph(tesla_data, tesla_revenue, 'Tesla')`.\n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    "    \n",
    "</details>\n"
   ]
